<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Presently" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Presently,</orth> immediately, on the spot: <cit><quote>who in their pride do p. abuse it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 864" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 864</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the moon being clouded p. is missed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 864" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 864</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>should p. extirpate me and mine,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.125" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 125</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>p.? Ay, with a twink,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.42.125" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 42</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>enforce them to this place, and p., I prithee,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.101.125" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 101</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>when you fasted, it was p. after dinner,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.1.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 1, 30</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I will send him hither to you p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.86" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 86</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>and then I'll p. attend you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.86" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 86</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.5.9" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 5, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.6.36" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 6, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.7.83" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 7, 83</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.7.83" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 7, 83</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.42" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 42</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.2.94" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 94</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.4.45" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.4.45" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 45</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tgv 5.2.45" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.95" default="NO" valid="ye